    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hi Friends üëã, Welcome To aGuideHub! ‚ù§Ô∏è To change mui textfield helper text color, set  in . It will change mui textfield helper text color. Today, I am going‚Ä¶","html":"<p>Hi Friends üëã,</p>\n<p>Welcome To aGuideHub! ‚ù§Ô∏è</p>\n<p>To change mui textfield helper text color, set <code class=\"language-text\">color: #783abc !important;</code> in <code class=\"language-text\">MuiFormHelperText-root</code>. It will change mui textfield helper text color.</p>\n<p>Today, I am going to show you, how to change mui textfield helper text color in react js.</p>\n<h2>Installation</h2>\n<p>Install the following packages to use mui textfield in react js.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">npm install @mui<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>material @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>react @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>styled</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">yarn add @mui<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>material @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>react @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>styled</code></pre></div>\n<h2>MUI material textfield changed helper text color example.</h2>\n<p>The below code is an example of changing helper text color using mui textfield.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Box <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@mui/material/Box'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> TextField <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@mui/material/TextField'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./App.css\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">InputWithIcon</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>firstName<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setFirstName<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Box m<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>TextField\n        label<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"First Name\"</span>\n        value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>firstName<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        helperText<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Some important text\"</span>\n        onChange<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token function\">setFirstName</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Box<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.css</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"> <span class=\"token selector\">.MuiFormHelperText-root</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #783abc <span class=\"token important\">!important</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>In the above code example, I have used the <code class=\"language-text\">@mui/material</code> TextField component and changed mui helper text color of MUI Textfield.</p>\n<p>Check the output of the above code example.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/61b4255a35f7ffd0339ab516b5d5953b/38f6f/helper-text-color.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.202531645569614%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"React, Mui Textfield Icon Button\"\n        title=\"React, Mui Textfield Icon Button\"\n        src=\"/static/61b4255a35f7ffd0339ab516b5d5953b/828fb/helper-text-color.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/61b4255a35f7ffd0339ab516b5d5953b/ff44c/helper-text-color.jpg 158w,\n/static/61b4255a35f7ffd0339ab516b5d5953b/a6688/helper-text-color.jpg 315w,\n/static/61b4255a35f7ffd0339ab516b5d5953b/828fb/helper-text-color.jpg 630w,\n/static/61b4255a35f7ffd0339ab516b5d5953b/0ede0/helper-text-color.jpg 945w,\n/static/61b4255a35f7ffd0339ab516b5d5953b/3ac88/helper-text-color.jpg 1260w,\n/static/61b4255a35f7ffd0339ab516b5d5953b/38f6f/helper-text-color.jpg 1366w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>All the best üëç</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"How to change mui textfield helper text color in react js?","tags":["React"],"date":"November 20, 2022","description":"Example of change mui textfield helper text color in React js with step by step tutorial - aGuideHub","social_image":"media/template/reactjs.jpg"}},"prev":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to change mui textfield helper text position in react js?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2022-11-20-how-to-change-mui-textfield-helper-text-position-in-react-js/"}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to use mui close icon in react js?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2022-11-20-how-to-use-mui-close-icon-in-react-js/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/2022-11-20-how-to-change-mui-textfield-helper-text-color-in-react-js/","prevSl